DSP- Digital Signal Processing

Communications Channel  Continued
=================================
	bits --> DSP --(x(0), x(1),...)--> n --(y(0),y(1),...)--> DSP --> bits

	y(n)=\sum_k h(k)x(n-k)

	There is interferance beetween symbols due to the echo effect.

	Solution: Build signal in frequency domain, convert to time domain, send through channel, convert back to frequency domain.

	bits --> IDFT --(x(0), x(1),...)--> n --(y(0),y(1),...)--> DFT --> bits

	Y_m = H(m/p 2\pi)X_m
